  1000	        action: "Transform the latest iteration graphEvents delta into review graph nodes and edges, then upsert it"
  1001	        read:
  1002	          - "{state_paths.state_log}"
  1003	          - "{state_paths.findings_registry}"
  1004	        transform: |
  1005	          1. Read the latest iteration JSONL record after reducer completion.
  1006	          2. If graphEvents is absent or empty, set graph_nodes_json = [] and graph_edges_json = [] and skip the upsert.
  1007	          3. For each graph event without relation/source/target, normalize type = uppercase(event.type || event.nodeKind || event.type) and keep only DIMENSION, FILE, FINDING, EVIDENCE, REMEDIATION, BUG_CLASS, INVARIANT, PRODUCER, CONSUMER, TEST.
  1008	          4. Emit nodes as { id, type, name, iteration, metadata } using the event label (or id fallback) and review metadata for run/current focus.
  1009	          5. For each graph event with relation + source + target, normalize relation = uppercase(event.relation) and keep only COVERS, EVIDENCE_FOR, CONTRADICTS, RESOLVES, CONFIRMS, ESCALATES, IN_DIMENSION, IN_FILE.
  1010	          6. Emit edges as { id, relation, sourceId, targetId, metadata } and deduplicate the batch by id.
  1011	          7. Discard malformed or unknown graph events instead of failing the review iteration.
  1012	        bash: "node .opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/upsert.cjs --spec-folder \"{spec_folder}\" --loop-type \"review\" --session-id \"{session_id}\" --nodes '{graph_nodes_json}' --edges '{graph_edges_json}'"
  1013	        note: "Invoke the runtime script directly. Upsert only the latest iteration graph delta."
  1014	        outputs:
  1015	          - graph_nodes_json: "JSON array of normalized review graph nodes for the latest iteration"
  1016	          - graph_edges_json: "JSON array of normalized review graph edges for the latest iteration"
  1017	        skip_conditions:
  1018	          - "Latest iteration record has no graphEvents array"
  1019	
  1020	      # ─── APPROVAL GATE: Post-Iteration ───

