tion/README.md:69:| `save-quality-gate.ts` | 3-layer pre-storage quality gate: structural validation, content quality scoring (title, triggers, length, anchors, metadata, signal density), and semantic dedup. Behind `SPECKIT_SAVE_QUALITY_GATE` flag with 14-day warn-only graduation period |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:85:| Uniqueness | No duplicate anchor IDs in same file |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:89:Two-tier duplicate detection:\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:125:| PF010 | DUPLICATE_DETECTED | Generic duplicate found |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:141:| `checkDuplicate` | `(params: DuplicateCheckParams, options?) => DuplicateCheckResult` | Detect duplicates |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:160:| Layer 2 | Content Quality | Weighted signal density across 5 dimensions (title 0.25, triggers 0.20, length 0.20, anchors 0.15, metadata 0.20). Threshold: 0.4 |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:175:| `scoreTriggerQuality(triggerPhrases)` | Layer 2 dimension: trigger phrase quality (0-1) |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:203:  check_duplicates: true,\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:258:  triggerPhrases: ['architecture', 'sqlite'],\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/validation/README.md:274:| Full validation | `runPreflight()` | Before memory_save |\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/index.ts:66:type MemoryTriggersModule = typeof import('./memory-triggers.js');\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/index.ts:74:type SessionLearningModule = typeof import('./session-learning.js');\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/index.ts:76:type CausalGraphModule = typeof import('./causal-graph.js');\\n