 vectors (naming convention: `context-index__<provider>__<model>__<dims>.sqlite`).\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/database/README.md:72:- Use MCP tools (`memory_stats`, `memory_health`, `memory_index_scan`) for normal operations.\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/database/README.md:73:- Structural reads (`code_graph_query`, `code_graph_context`) can perform bounded inline selective refresh against `code-graph.sqlite` when the stale set is small enough.\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/database/README.md:74:- Empty or broadly stale structural states still require explicit `code_graph_scan` to rebuild the graph database.\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:4:// status/percentage contradiction, and topical coherence path normalization.\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:23:  triggerPhrases?: string[];\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:32:  if (opts.triggerPhrases && opts.triggerPhrases.length > 0) {\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:33:    lines.push('trigger_phrases:');\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:34:    for (const tp of opts.triggerPhrases) {\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:63:function createTempSpecFolder(triggerPhrases: string[]): string {\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:70:    'trigger_phrases:',\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:71:    ...triggerPhrases.map(tp => `  - \\\"${tp}\\\"`),\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:98:    it('unclosed single-quoted string triggers V13 failure', () => {\\n.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/tests/validation-v13-v14-v12.vitest.ts:107:    it('unclosed dou